pageTitle: The Sunday Briefing: Casey Jarzabek Makes Back-To-Back Sunday Million Final Tables | PokerNews
textBeforeTable: PokerStars Sunday Million ($1M Guaranteed) Others to score big on Sunday were Kevin "Civell" Vandersmissen, Grayson "swish3113" Ramage, Alex "AD_84" Debus, Brandon "oncommand" Meyers, and Pius "MastaP89" Heinz. Over at Full Tilt Poker, MiniFTOPS XXI concluded with Caio "Pessagno" Pessagno winning the Main Event for $120,270. He bested a final table that included Thiago "DecanoBR" Nishijima, Mike "GoLeafsGoEh" Leah and Daniel "dDeoxyribo" Strelitz. A busy weekend on the virtual felt saw nine players earn six figures in tournament action. Leading the nine is PokerStars Sunday Million winner "stackarn" with $164,000 following a five-handed deal. Finishing third was Casey "bigdogpckt5s" Jarzabek, fresh off of a fourth-place finish in last week's Sunday Million. In addition, Jarzabek won the Super Tuesday less than two weeks ago.
